{"title":"Heavy Bikes Get a Boost with the REMCO Bike Lift System","link":"https://bikerumor.com/heavy-bikes-get-a-boost-with-the-remco-bike-lift-system/","date":1699475791000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"853\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero.jpeg\" alt=\"REMCO Tools Bike Lift hero\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero.jpeg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero-720x480.jpeg 720w\" /></p>\n<p>REMCO Tools was founded to provide solutions to quickly and comfortably service bicycles of all shapes and sizes. pairing design and function, they <a href=\"https://remcotools.prezly.com/introducing-remco-tools-innovative-and-powerful-bike-lift-system\">created something unique</a> in the Bike Lift system. REMCO claims the Bike Lift is the “first-of-its-kind for cycling enthusiasts, professional mechanics, and bike shops.”</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-close-up.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-close-up-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"REMCO Tools Bike Lift close up\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-close-up-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-close-up-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-close-up-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-close-up-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-close-up-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-close-up.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo/REMCO Tools)</figcaption></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-townie.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-townie-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"REMCO Tools Bike Lift townie\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-townie-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-townie-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-townie-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-townie-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-townie-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-townie.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-cargo-bike.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-cargo-bike-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"REMCO Tools Bike Lift cargo bike\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-cargo-bike-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-cargo-bike-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-cargo-bike-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-cargo-bike-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-cargo-bike-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-cargo-bike.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The automated Bike Lift system is <a href=\"https://www.remcotools.com/\">REMCO</a>‘s flagship product. It boasts a small footprint, making it space-efficient for small work areas. It carries with it a hearty lifting capacity of 100 pounds, so eBikes and some cargo bikes are not an issue. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-Enduro.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-Enduro-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"REMCO Tools Bike Lift Enduro\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-Enduro-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-Enduro-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-Enduro-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-Enduro-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-Enduro-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-Enduro.jpeg 1280w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"533\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"REMCO Tools Bike Lift hero\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero-800x533.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero-297x198.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero-120x80.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero-768x512.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero-720x480.jpeg 720w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-hero.jpeg 1280w\" /></a><figcaption>(Photo/REMCO Tools)</figcaption></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The lift can be raised or lowered to provide easier access to every part of the bike and help keep the area of repair in a comfortable position for the mechanic. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>At the center of the Bike Lift is a motorized lifting column, providing a substantial vertical adjustment range. Starting at the fully collapsed position of 33.75″, the Bike Lift can then be fully extended to an impressive 59.75″. This offers over 2 feet of vertical height adjustment. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-orange-clamp.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-orange-clamp-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"REMCO Tools Bike Lift orange clamp\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-clamp.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-clamp-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"REMCO Tools Bike Lift clamp\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-blue-clamp.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-blue-clamp-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"REMCO Tools Bike Lift blue clamp\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-red-clamp.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-red-clamp-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"REMCO Tools Bike Lift red clamp\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-proclamp.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-proclamp-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"REMCO Tools Bike Lift proclamp\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-Park-clamp.jpeg\"><img src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-Park-clamp-800x533.jpeg\" alt=\"REMCO Tools Bike Lift Park clamp\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p>It is modular and backward compatible with a pretty wide range of existing repair stand clamps allowing you to, more than likely, use your current equipment and favorite clamping method. </p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-programable.jpeg\"><img width=\"600\" height=\"600\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-programable.jpeg\" alt=\"REMCO Tools Bike Lift programable\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-programable.jpeg 600w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-programable-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/11/REMCO-Tools-Bike-Lift-programable-120x120.jpeg 120w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Bike Lift can also be used with its three memory presets, allowing you to put the stand at your desired height with the touch of a button. There is also a control lock that keeps others from using the stand. You can also switch between Metric and US Customary units on the display. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>The Bike Lift Features &amp; Retail</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>Retail: Starts at $555</p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Compact and space-saving design</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Three customizable height presets</li>\n\n\n\n<li>100lb weight capacity (Cargo bikes excluded)</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Durable construction for long-lasting reliability</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Modular &amp; backward compatible with a wide range of existing repair stands and clamps</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<p>Bike Lift will start shipping to North America on December 18, 2023. Shipping to Europe will start in early Summer 2024. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://www.remcotools.com/\">RemcoTools.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/heavy-bikes-get-a-boost-with-the-remco-bike-lift-system/\">Heavy Bikes Get a Boost with the REMCO Bike Lift System</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Ron Frazelle","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"20ddf2b14e74170a39c42f065726d490009255b66da5b4fd79d4612946897776","category":"Cycling"}